dc_title_s: Roads and ROW St. Croix County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent roads and Right of Ways (ROW) for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NSt_Croix_Roads_ROW_2018.gdbN. [The areas of land that are managed for the real estate tax system, these may be multipart polygons, all have a unique tax key number.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: St. Croix County Land Use, Planning and Development
